data.description: Welcome to PARADISE! This beautiful GULF ACCESS POOL HOME offers 3 Beds + Den, 3 FULL BATHS, and a spacious open floor plan. It was formerly a model home for Villa Homes with Southern Exposure. The kitchen features custom cabinetry, a Reverse Osmosis system, and a whole-home water softener. Vaulted ceilings grace the great room, while the master bedroom boasts a tray ceiling with elegant lighting and French doors leading to the lanai. One guest bedroom is an ensuite and also has access to the lanai.  Custom light fixtures illuminate the entire house, including the yard and lanai. The Master Bedroom and Bathroom have been tastefully remodeled with dual sinks, a walk-in shower (ADA ACCESSIBLE), a soaking tub, and his and her walk-in closets. Relax by the pool on the large lanai with Travertine surrounded by mature landscaping. The pool has a beautiful mosaic tile finish and a composite dock with a 10K lb boat lift. Safety is ensured with impact windows, accordion and electric hurricane shutters, and a recently upgraded garage door. Other updates include a BRAND NEW $72K METAL TILE ROOF (2023), a LANAI, POOL CAGE & SCREENS(2023), and a 5-ton AC System (2020). Enjoy stunning sunsets on your dock, embracing the best of SWFL living in this lovely retreat.
